// each char table is specific for each display and maps all numbers/symbols
// needed:
//   - pos 0-9   - Numbers from 0 to 9
//   - pos 10    - Space " "
//   - pos 11    - minus symbol "-"
//   - pos 12    - degree symbol "°"
//   - pos 13    - equal "="
//   - pos 14    - triple lines "/"
//   - pos 15    - underscore "_"
//   - pos 16-41 - Letters from A to Z
